s the Perfect Kindle for You"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;Amazon's &lt;a href="http://lifehacker.com/5844640/amazon-introduces-kindle-fire-touch-tablet-79-kindles-and-more"&gt;newly introduced&lt;/a&gt; Kindles, including the Fire tablet, vary by quite a few features and certain options add more to the price. How to decide which Kindle to get? Just check this flowchart for your options. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Michael Degusta, writing at The Understatement, counts at least 11 different features across the new Kindles. Drill down to find which features and prices affect you. (Click to expand):&lt;br&gt;
